91void CreateNetworkConnectionToWebProcess::callReply(IPC::Decoder& decoder, CompletionHandler<void(std::optional<IPC::Attachment>&&, WebCore::HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy&&)>&& completionHandler)
92{
93 std::optional<std::optional<IPC::Attachment>> connectionIdentifier;
94 decoder >> connectionIdentifier;
95 if (!connectionIdentifier) {
96 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
97 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
98 return;
99 }
100 std::optional<WebCore::HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy> cookieAcceptPolicy;
101 decoder >> cookieAcceptPolicy;
102 if (!cookieAcceptPolicy) {
103 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
104 cancelReply(WTFMove(completionHandler));
105 return;
106 }
107 completionHandler(WTFMove(*connectionIdentifier), WTFMove(*cookieAcceptPolicy));
108}
109
110void CreateNetworkConnectionToWebProcess::cancelReply(CompletionHandler<void(std::optional<IPC::Attachment>&&, WebCore::HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy&&)>&& completionHandler)
111{
112 completionHandler(IPC::AsyncReplyError<std::optional<IPC::Attachment>>::create(), IPC::AsyncReplyError<WebCore::HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy>::create());
113}
114
115void CreateNetworkConnectionToWebProcess::send(UniqueRef<IPC::Encoder>&& encoder, IPC::Connection& connection, const std::optional<IPC::Attachment>& connectionIdentifier, WebCore::HTTPCookieAcceptPolicy cookieAcceptPolicy)
116{
117 encoder.get() << connectionIdentifier;
118 encoder.get() << cookieAcceptPolicy;
119 connection.sendSyncReply(WTFMove(encoder));
120}

753#if ENABLE(RESOURCE_LOAD_STATISTICS)
754
755void DomainIDExistsInDatabase::callReply(IPC::Decoder& decoder, CompletionHandler<void(bool&&)>&& completionHandler)
756{
757 std::optional<bool> exists;

1945{
1946 auto protectedThis = makeRef(*this);
1947 if (decoder.messageName() == Messages::NetworkProcess::InitializeNetworkProcess::name())
1948 return IPC::handleMessage<Messages::NetworkProcess::InitializeNetworkProcess>(decoder, this, &NetworkProcess::initializeNetworkProcess);
1949 if (decoder.messageName() == Messages::NetworkProcess::CreateNetworkConnectionToWebProcess::name())
1950 return IPC::handleMessageAsync<Messages::NetworkProcess::CreateNetworkConnectionToWebProcess>(connection, decoder, this, &NetworkProcess::createNetworkConnectionToWebProcess);
1951#if USE(SOUP)
